{"word":"ἑκάς","slug":"ἑκάς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑκάς</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>far, afar, far off</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>procul</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>; <el>οὐχ ἑκάς</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>far from, far away from</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; also, <el>ἑκὰς ἀπὸ τοῦ τείχεος</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>ἑκαστέρω</el>, <i>farther</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; also <el>ἑκαστοτέρω</el> <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>ἑκαστάτω</el>, <i>farthest</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἑκαστάτω τινός</el> <i>farthest from . .</i> , <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of Time, <el>οὐχ ἑκὰς χρόνου</el> in no <i>long</i> time, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}